{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-076", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 76.1", "sort_key": "076.001", "text_original": "人之生也柔弱，其死也堅強。萬物草木之生也柔脆，其死也枯槁。故堅強者死之徒，柔弱者生之徒。是以兵強則不勝，", "text_normalized": "人之生也柔弱，其死也堅強。萬物草木之生也柔脆，其死也枯槁。故堅強者死之徒，柔弱者生之徒。是以兵強則不勝，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-076", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 76.2", "sort_key": "076.002", "text_original": "木強則兵。", "text_normalized": "木強則兵。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-076", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 76.3", "sort_key": "076.003", "text_original": "強大處下，", "text_normalized": "強大處下，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-076", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-076__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 76.4", "sort_key": "076.004", "text_original": "柔弱處上。", "text_normalized": "柔弱處上。", "notes": ""}
